                              'Uconec' 1.0

                           by Charles-N. Jacob

  'Uconec' is a @{" Workbench game " link play} in which you have to connect pairs
of 'U' shaped tiles together so the 'open' portion of a tile faces
the open portion of a neighbouring tile. You get 1 point for each
pair of tiles that are connected together, if both tiles are of the
same colour, you get more points.

  One important thing: do NOT isolate any tile...

  Have fun!

